OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with sunny spells, perhaps
OL,7,Fstill cloudy around western areas.
OL,8,FCloud developing later in the night
OL,9,Fwith a few spots of rain possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FMostly cloudy with bright
OL,12,Fspells. Mainly dry in the morning, a
OL,13,Ffew afternoon showers developing and
OL,14,Fthese turning sharp in places.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,17,Fbright start on Monday but a few
OL,18,Fshowers developing and cloudy at
OL,19,Ftimes. Remaining settled on Tuesday
OL,20,Fand Wednesday with bright or sunny
OL,21,Fspells and light winds.
